Package: facpart
Title: Facet Theory Partitioning of 2D Configurations
Version: 0.1.1
Date: 2026-06-05
Authors@R:
    c(person("Hans-Ruediger", "Pfister", email = "rpfister57@gmail.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-3802-4222")),
      person("Claude Code", "AI", role = c("ctb")))
Maintainer: Hans-Ruediger Pfister <rpfister57@gmail.com>
Description: Tools for partitioning 2-dimensional configurations (such as
    multidimensional-scaling output) according to facet theory, supporting axial (parallel
    lines), radial (nested circles or ellipses), and angular (wedge-shaped)
    partitions.
